Description:
    Generate vue initializer for rails views.

Example:
    rails g espresso:vue3:initializer comment::comment_list_table

    This will create:
        app/javascript/src/application/js/vue_initializer/comment/comment_list_table.js

    By default, the scope will be `application`, if you want to generate
    initializer in different scope, using 2nd argument to make option.

    e.g.
    rails g espresso:vue:initializer comment::comment_list_table admin

    This will create:
        app/javascript/src/admin/js/vue_initializer/comment/comment_list_table.js
